ֲ ֲ ֲ ֲ In halls, in gay attire is seen;
ֲ ֲ ֲ ֲ In hamlets, dances on the green.
ֲ ֲ ֲ ֲ Love rules the court, the camp, the grove,
ֲ ֲ ֲ ֲ And men below and saints above;
